# M2DG v1 — APP MASTER PRD (Full Build)

## 1) Vision
M2DG connects hoopers worldwide through real-world court activity, challenges, leaderboards, and community growth.

## 2) Platforms
- Primary: iOS (first) then Android
- Dev: Flutter Web for speed

## 3) MVP Release Strategy
We build feature-by-feature and take each to “launch-ready” before moving on.

Launch-ready means:
- Clean UX (no dev-looking screens)
- Stable state handling (loading/empty/error)
- Navigation complete (no dead ends)
- Works on mobile screen sizes
- No console spam / no crashes

## 4) Feature Modules (Full App Scope)

### A) Auth + Onboarding
- Sign in / Sign up
- Profile setup
- Basic onboarding tutorial

### B) Courts (Current Focus)
- Courts list + search/sort/filter
- Court details
- Check-in validation (radius + cooldown)
- Court “home court” selection (later phase)
Status: IN PROGRESS

### C) Challenges (Core Gameplay)
- Challenge types (1v1, 3pt, FT, team)
- Create/join challenge
- Score reporting
- Dispute flow (later phase)

### D) Leaderboards
- Court leaderboard
- Global leaderboard
- “Court Champ” logic

### E) Player Profiles
- Public profile
- Stats + badges
- Win streaks

### F) Notifications
- In-app notifications
- Push notifications (later)

### G) Moderation / Reporting
- Report a user
- Report a court
- Flag suspicious check-ins

### H) Admin (Later)
- Court management
- Content moderation
- Analytics

## 5) Non-Goals for MVP
- Live streaming
- Payments/merch
- Full social feed
(These can be v2)

## 6) Data/Backend
- Supabase (Auth, DB, RLS)
- Future: Edge functions for rate limiting & business logic

## 7) App Navigation (High-Level)
- Tab/Nav structure:
  - Courts
  - Challenges
  - Leaderboard
  - Profile
  - Settings
